title: Star Wars - A New Hope [Theatrical] (4;3-LTBX VHS2DVD).iso
description:
Star Wars A New Hope
--------------------

Transfered from the 1996 VHS Letterbox release (digitally remastered).  This is NOT the Special Edition.

The video is 4:3 letterboxed (you&#039;ll get two sets of bars on a widescreen display, horizontal and vertical) but Greedo doesn&#039;t shoot and there are no cartoonish droids flying around Mos Eisley.

Grainy due to the source being VHS.
